Encode/Arabic/ArabTeX/ZDMG version 1.06            2004/02/13 23:26:56
=======================================

Perl extension for ZDMG phonetic transcription of Arabic using the
ArabTeX notation


INSTALLATION

To install this module on 'make-aware' systems, type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

With ActiveState Perl, use the Perl Package Manager instead.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Encode::Arabic::ArabTeX, Encode::Mapper,
    Encode, Encode::Encoding


